  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d85\u0db1\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca 02\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "02 killed in bus accident",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Pussellawa police said that two passengers on the bus were killed and 08 others who were traveling on the bus were injured and admitted to the Pussellawa hospital.",
        "This accident happened today (11th) near Kachamale Kambi Vatunivasa Pela on Pussellawa Pretrasi road.",
        "Due to a mechanical fault in the front wheel of the bus that was running, the driver tried to stop the bus, causing the bus to hit a mound of earth on the side of the road and the bus was stopped.",
        "The police said that two people who were traveling on the bus board died on the spot.",
        "Suranjith Pushpakumar (39) and Vijaya Kumar (26) who are residents of Pussellawa Pretrasi estate have died in the accident.",
        "The police said that a large number of people were traveling in the bus at the time of the accident, and the driver fled after the accident, and an operation has been launched to arrest the driver.",
        "After the accident, an enraged group set fire to the bus and destroyed it. The Pussellawa police are conducting further investigations regarding the accident."
      ],
